title: GRMLN perform "Do You Know How It Feels?" - Converse Rubber Tracks: Ready, Set
description:
Recent Carpark Records signee GRMLN stopped by Converse Rubber Tracks San Francisco to perform a new track off the recently released record "Empire." We followed Yoodoo Park from his base in Santa Cruz up the Pacific Coast Highway to San Francisco. Joined by his brother Tae San Park on bass and Keith Frerichs on drums, the band performed a driven version of "Do You Know How It Feels?" - a perfect complement to a sunny, windy day in Cali. 
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
